Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.76,Main01,KAGURA,0,0,0,,!لا تعرقلني
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.14,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,...هذا
